Step-1: 
===========
Download Dart SDK. Download Dart SDK from the Dart SDK archive page.

click on DART SDK to download SDK windows 64-bit Architecture, the download will start and a zip file will be downloaded.

Note: To download SDK for any other os select os of your choice.

